MARBLE HILL SPRING 2018 TENNIS PROGRAMME
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Now in its 6th year, the tennis classes in Marble Hill Park start
    next week and cater for children aged 4-15 years and over.

    The classes are for children who are new to the game, and children
    who have had some previous experience of coaching. The classes run
    for 5-6 weeks, and the maximum class size is 8 children (4 children
    per. court).

