PRIMARY SCHOOL OFFERS DAY 2018
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Ninety eight percent of in-borough applicants have been offered a
    place at one of their first three preferred primary schools.

    On 16 April, Richmond Council made the initial allocation
    of Reception class offers for this September. This year, 2,174
    pupils applied for a place - compared with 2,363 last year.

